* [
Turritella ( Oligodia ) Archimedis Brong.
] var. abundans— Handmann, 1882: 217 .

Studied material. 8 spec. NHMW 2013/0479/0771, 28 spec. NHMW 1997z0178/1363,
8 spec. NHMW 1989/0037/0002, Gainfarn ( Austria )
;
